name: IDOR
description:
If there are any bugs, please let me know in the comments!

The HTML port of this game might have an input issue. If you cannot move, try refreshing your browser and typing one of these passwords to continue from a checkpoint. Sorry for the issue, it's my first time exporting for HTML.

Checkpoint passwords:

AB23 : Level 3B

ABC1: Level 4

ACB6 : Level 6

BOSS : Level 7 (Boss fight)
